# 1. What is Deployment?

## Definition

Deployment is the process of moving a software application from your local computer to an online server so that anyone can access it through the Internet.

Before deployment

```text
Your Computer

↓

localhost:5000
```

After deployment

```text
https://salarypredictor.onrender.com
```

Now anyone can access your application.

---

## Real-Time Examples

Applications available online:

- Gmail
- Amazon
- Netflix
- Facebook
- Flipkart
- Odoo ERP

These applications are deployed on cloud servers.

---

## Answer

Deployment makes a web application available online for users around the world.

---

# 2. Why Do We Need Deployment?

Without deployment,

only your computer can access the application.

Example

```text
http://localhost:5000
```

Only you can open it.

After deployment,

everyone can access the application using a public URL.

---

## Answer

Deployment allows users to access the application from anywhere using the Internet.

---

