# 10. Upload Project to GitHub

## Step 1

Initialize Git.

```bash
git init
```

---

## Step 2

Add all files.

```bash
git add .
```

---

## Step 3

Commit changes.

```bash
git commit -m "Initial Commit"
```

---

## Step 4

Connect GitHub repository.

```bash
git remote add origin <repository_url>
```

---

## Step 5

Push code.

```bash
git push -u origin main
```

---

## Answer

GitHub stores your project online and allows Render to access it.

