# 11. Deploy on Render

Deployment Steps

1. Login to Render.

2. Click **New Web Service**.

3. Connect your GitHub account.

4. Select the repository.

5. Configure the project.

---

## Settings

Environment

```text
Python 3
```

Build Command

```text
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Start Command

```text
gunicorn app:app
```

---

## Click

```text
Deploy Web Service
```

---

## Answer

Render automatically installs dependencies and starts the Flask application.

---

