# 14. Common Deployment Errors

| Error | Solution |
|--------|----------|
| ModuleNotFoundError | Add missing package to requirements.txt |
| Build Failed | Check requirements.txt and Python version |
| App Crashed | Verify Procfile and app.py |
| File Not Found | Check file paths |
| Model Not Loading | Ensure `salary_model.pkl` is included |

---

## Answer

Most deployment issues occur due to missing files, incorrect package versions, or configuration errors.

